---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Compass Report Newsletter | Compass Score">
  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-emerald-50 to-white min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="text-6xl mb-4">📧</div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">The Compass Report</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-[#CBD5E1] max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Weekly insights on quality stocks, delivered straight to your inbox.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Main CTA Box -->
      <div class="bg-[#161B24] rounded-2xl border-2 border-[#22D3EE] shadow-xl p-8 mb-12">
        <div class="md:flex md:items-center md:justify-between gap-8">
          <div class="mb-6 md:mb-0">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Subscribe for just $5/month</h2>
            <p class="text-[#CBD5E1]">
              Join thousands of investors who start their week with The Compass Report.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <a href="#subscribe" class="block bg-[#22D3EE] hover:bg-[#06B6D4] text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg transition text-center">
              Subscribe Now
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- What You Get -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-8">What You'll Get Every Week</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-[#161B24] border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.06)] rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-3">📊</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Top Quality Picks</h3>
            <p class="text-[#CBD5E1] text-sm">
              5-10 handpicked stocks with high Compass Scores that caught our attention this week.
              Full analysis of why they made the list.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-[#161B24] border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.06)] rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-3">🔔</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Score Changes Alert</h3>
            <p class="text-[#CBD5E1] text-sm">
              Notable upgrades and downgrades across the market. Know when quality metrics
              are shifting before everyone else.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-[#161B24] border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.06)] rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-3">📈</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Sector Deep Dives</h3>
            <p class="text-[#CBD5E1] text-sm">
              Monthly analysis of quality trends across different sectors. Identify
              where the best opportunities are hiding.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-[#161B24] border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.06)] rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-3">🎓</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Investor Education</h3>
            <p class="text-[#CBD5E1] text-sm">
              Learn how to use quality metrics in your own analysis. Tips, strategies,
              and real examples from experienced investors.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Sample Newsletter -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Sample Newsletter</h2>
        <div class="bg-[#080A0F] border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.06)] rounded-2xl p-8">
          <div class="border-b border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.06)] pb-6 mb-6">
            <div class="text-sm text-[#64748B] mb-2">Week of February 24, 2025</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">The Compass Report #47</h3>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-[#22D3EE] mb-2">🌟 Top Pick This Week: NVIDIA (NVDA)</h4>
              <p class="text-[#CBD5E1] text-sm">
                Compass Score: 87 (Grade A). Despite the hype, NVIDIA's fundamentals remain rock solid.
                Strong cash flow generation combined with exceptional profitability makes this a quality
                holding for long-term investors...
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">📊 Score Movers</h4>
              <p class="text-[#CBD5E1] text-sm">
                <strong>Upgrades:</strong> META (82→89), UNH (76→83), HD (71→78)<br/>
                <strong>Downgrades:</strong> TSLA (34→29), SMCI (18→11), COIN (45→38)
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2">🎯 Sector Spotlight: Healthcare</h4>
              <p class="text-[#CBD5E1] text-sm">
                Healthcare continues to show strong quality metrics. Average sector score of 62 vs.
                market average of 48. Top picks: UNH, JNJ, LLY...
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.06)] text-center text-sm text-[#64748B]">
            This is a preview. Subscribe to get the full newsletter every week.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Subscribe Form -->
      <div id="subscribe" class="bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Start Your Subscription</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mb-6">$5/month. Cancel anytime. First week free.</p>

        <form class="max-w-md mx-auto">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
            <input
              type="email"
              placeholder="Enter your email"
              class="flex-grow px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border-0 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#22D3EE]"
              required
            />
            <button
              type="submit"
              class="bg-[#22D3EE] hover:bg-[#06B6D4] text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition"
            >
              Subscribe
            </button>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-[#64748B] mt-4">
            By subscribing, you agree to our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy.
          </p>
        </form>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonials -->
      <div class="mt-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-8">What Subscribers Say</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-[#161B24] border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.06)] rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1 text-amber-400 mb-3">
              <span>★★★★★</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[#CBD5E1] text-sm mb-4">
              "The weekly picks have been consistently good. Found several quality stocks
              I never would have discovered on my own."
            </p>
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold">— Michael T.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-[#161B24] border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.06)] rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1 text-amber-400 mb-3">
              <span>★★★★★</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[#CBD5E1] text-sm mb-4">
              "Best $5 I spend each month. The score change alerts have helped me avoid
              some real disasters."
            </p>
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold">— Sarah K.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-[#161B24] border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.06)] rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1 text-amber-400 mb-3">
              <span>★★★★★</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[#CBD5E1] text-sm mb-4">
              "Clear, actionable insights without the noise. I look forward to it every
              Sunday evening."
            </p>
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold">— David R.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ -->
      <div class="mt-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Questions</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          <div class="bg-[#161B24] border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.06)] rounded-xl p-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">When is the newsletter sent?</h3>
            <p class="text-[#CBD5E1] text-sm">
              Every Sunday evening (EST), so you're ready for the week ahead.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-[#161B24] border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.06)] rounded-xl p-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Can I cancel anytime?</h3>
            <p class="text-[#CBD5E1] text-sm">
              Yes! No contracts, no commitments. Cancel with one click from your account.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-[#161B24] border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.06)] rounded-xl p-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Is this financial advice?</h3>
            <p class="text-[#CBD5E1] text-sm">
              No. The Compass Report is for educational and informational purposes only.
              Always do your own research before making investment decisions.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
